---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { totalToolCount } from '../data/tools';
---

<Layout
  title="About Neetab | Neat Tools. One Tab."
  description="Neetab is a free online tool hub built for people who just want things to work. No sign-ups, no bloat, no BS."
  path="/about"
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-10 animate-fade-in">
    <h1 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-6">
      About Neetab
    </h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-surface-700 dark:text-surface-300 leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">What is Neetab?</h2>
        <p>Neetab is a free hub of {totalToolCount}+ online tools built to make everyday tasks faster and simpler.
          PDF converters, image compressors, calculators, color tools, AI writing assistants, developer utilities -
          everything in one place, no account required.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Why we built it</h2>
        <p>Most online tool sites are slow, plastered with ads, and ask you to sign up before you can do anything.
          We built Neetab because we wanted the opposite: tools that load instantly, work on the first try, and
          respect your time and privacy. Simple as that.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">How it works</h2>
        <p>Most tools on Neetab run entirely in your browser. No files are uploaded, nothing leaves your device.
          A small number of tools (PDF conversion, AI writing tools) send data to a backend server for processing -
          we delete everything immediately after and never store your content.
          The full details are in our <a href="/privacy" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Free forever?</h2>
        <p>Yes. Every tool is free to use with no sign-up. We keep the lights on through non-intrusive advertising.
          We do not sell your data. We do not have a premium tier. We do not plan to change this.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Built with</h2>
        <p>Astro, React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS on the frontend. FastAPI + LibreOffice + pdf2docx on the backend.
          Hosted on Vercel (frontend) and Railway (backend). AI tools use Google Gemini and Groq.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 mb-2">Get in touch</h2>
        <p>Tool requests, bug reports, feedback, partnerships - we read everything.
          Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@neetab.com" class="text-brand-500 font-medium hover:underline">hello@neetab.com</a>
          or visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">contact page</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>
